HEADWORD: Herdbook
<hw>Herd"book`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A book containing
the list and pedigrees of one or more herds of choice breeds of cattle;
-- also called <altname>herd record</altname>, or <altname>herd
register</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

